OL,4,CFace masks no longer required in
OL,5,Cclassrooms
OL,6, Face masks will no longer be required
OL,7, in secondary school classrooms in
OL,8, England after 17 May, the Prime
OL,9, Minister Boris Johnson has confirmed.
OL,11,FFace coverings have been recommended
OL,12,Fsince the return to school in March -
OL,13,Fbut that will end as part of the
OL,14,Fphasing out of lockdown measures.
OL,16,FThere have been concerns that masks
OL,17,Fobstruct communicating and learning.
OL,19,FBut head teachers warned the decision
OL,20,Fto remove masks was "hard to reconcile"
OL,21,Fwith the evidence on safety.
